#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.128"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.128:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.128:0.2"
msgid "13. Gilānavagga "
msgstr "13. Sick "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: samaṇadukkha-sukhasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.128:0.3"
msgid "128. Samaṇasukhasutta "
msgstr "128. An Ascetic’s Happiness "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.128:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, samaṇadukkhāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five kinds of suffering for an ascetic. "

msgctxt "an5.128:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.128:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu asantuṭṭho hoti itarītarena cīvarena, asantuṭṭho hoti itarītarena piṇḍapātena, asantuṭṭho hoti itarītarena senāsanena, asantuṭṭho hoti itarītarena gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena, anabhirato ca brahmacariyaṃ carati. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is not content with any kind of robe, alms-food, lodging, and medicines and supplies for the sick. And they live the spiritual life dissatisfied. "

msgctxt "an5.128:1.4"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca samaṇadukkhāni. "
msgstr "These are five kinds of suffering for an ascetic. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.128:2.1"
msgid "Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, samaṇasukhāni. "
msgstr "There are these five kinds of happiness for an ascetic. "

msgctxt "an5.128:2.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.128:2.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu santuṭṭho hoti itarītarena cīvarena, santuṭṭho hoti itarītarena piṇḍapātena, santuṭṭho hoti itarītarena senāsanena, santuṭṭho hoti itarītarena gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena, abhirato ca brahmacariyaṃ carati. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is content with any kind of robe, alms-food, lodging, and medicines and supplies for the sick. And they live the spiritual life satisfied. "

msgctxt "an5.128:2.4"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca samaṇasukhānī”ti. "
msgstr "These are five kinds of happiness for an ascetic.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.128:2.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
